r de la frontera de un tema ‘episódico’ nuevo. En segundo lugar, se describen sistemáticamente las diferentes funciones pragmáticas (foco, diferentes tipos de tópico) que asumen los pronombres sujeto en la interfaz sintáctico-prosódica. De este modo, el presente trabajo constituye una contribución importante al estudio de las características sintácticas y prosódicas de los sujetos pronominales explícitos en el habla espontánea de una variedad del español.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aSpanish languagexPronominals. 0aSpanish languagexProvincialismszArgentinazBuenos Aires. 4aInformationsstruktur. 4aNull-Subjekt-Sprache. 4aSubjektpronomina. 4aSyntax-Prosodie Schnittstelle. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Syntax.2bisacsh  aInformation Structure.  aPorteño Spanish.  aPronominal Subjects.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1z978311076251808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2015z9783110438710oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831104164590 cprintz978311041575940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311041639840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110416398423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110416398/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-076251-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSPb2015